{{About|the <code>timedAction</code> parameter used in crafting recipes|the timed actions used in the game|Timed Actions}}
The <code>timedAction</code> parameter is used to define the action animation played during the crafting process. The timed action is defined by the following format:
{{CodeSnip
| lang = lua
| code =
timedAction = <action name>,
}}

