Actions are defined in [[AnimSets]] in the category <code>actions</code> for the player animations.

{{Note|While unconfirmed, it is likely possible to create your own timed actions by creating new ones in the AnimSets.}}

==Example==
{{CodeSnip
| lang = lua
| code =
timedAction = Making,
}}